manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "dicom-rst"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "dicom-rst"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
description = "A blazingly fast DICOMweb implementation"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["dicom", "dicomweb", "healthcare"]
categories = ["multimedia"]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://gitlab.ume.de/ship/dicom-rst"
rust-version = "1.74.0"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
async-stream = "0.3.5"
async-trait = "0.1.74"
axum-macros = "0.4.1"
bytes = "1.5.0"
futures = "0.3.29"
http-body-util = "0.1"
log = "0.4.20"
mime = "0.3.17"
multer = "3.0.0"
pin-project = "1.1.5"
rand = "0.8.5"
serde_json = "1.0.108"
thiserror = "1.0.50"
tracing = "0.1.40"

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.7.4"
features = ["multipart"]

[dependencies.axum-extra]
version = "0.9.2"
features = ["query"]

[dependencies.axum-streams]
version = "0.12.0"
features = ["json"]

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.5.4"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.config]
version = "0.13.4"
features = ["toml"]

[dependencies.dicom]
git = "https://github.com/Enet4/dicom-rs"
rev = "6e020ec"

[dependencies.dicom-json]
git = "https://github.com/Enet4/dicom-rs"
rev = "6e020ec"

[dependencies.http-body]
version = "1.0.0"
features = []

[dependencies.hyper]
version = "1.1.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.hyper-util]
version = "0.1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.sentry]
version = "0.32.2"
features = ["tracing"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.193"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.35.1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower]
version = "0.4.13"
features = ["limit"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.5.0"
features = ["trace", "cors", "timeout"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.18"
features = ["env-filter"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.6.1"
features = ["v4"]

[profile.release]
opt-level = 3
lto = "fat"
codegen-units = 1
strip = "debuginfo"

[profile.release.package]
